window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From legendary fantasy author Gene Wolfe comes </b><b><i>The Knight,</i></b><b> the first half of the Wizard Knight duology, now for the first time in audio. </b>&nbsp;</p> <p>A young man in his teens is transported from our world to a magical realm that contains seven levels of reality. Very quickly transformed by magic into a grown man of heroic proportions, he takes the name Able and sets out on a quest to find the sword that has been promised to him, a sword he will get from a dragon, the one very special blade that will help him fulfill his life ambition to become a knight and a true hero.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Inside, however, Able remains a boy, and he must grow in every sense to survive the dangers and delights that lie ahead in encounters with giants, elves, wizards, and dragons. His adventure will conclude in the second installment of The Wizard Knight, <i>The Wizard</i>.</p>"; 
